title: Build Your Deck 5X Faster and Easier | DIY for Beginners
description:
Today we're building a ground level deck using the CAMO block system, pressure treated joists and Trex deck boards. This is a very straight forward project that anyone can tackle, the CAMO system makes your composite deck build faster and easier - its perfect for the DIYer. Cheers!
